---
const heroImage =
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2200&q=85';
---

<section
  class="hero"
  style={`background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(247,251,255,0.98) 0%, rgba(247,251,255,0.84) 31%, rgba(247,251,255,0.22) 58%, rgba(247,251,255,0.02) 100%), url(${heroImage}); background-size: cover; background-position: center right;`}
>
  <div class="hero__inner site-container">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <h1 class="hero__title">
        つくるだけでなく、<br />進化し続けるものを。
      </h1>
      <p class="hero__lead">
        保守性の高いシステム設計とプロダクト思考で、<br />
        長く価値を生むフロントエンド開発を。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .hero {
    min-height: 680px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #f1f5f9;

    &__inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 680px;
      padding-top: 80px;
    }

    &__content {
      padding-bottom: 48px;
    }

    &__title {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--color-ink);
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 650;
    }

    &__lead {
      margin: 32px 0 0;
      color: #1e293b;
      font-weight: 650;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: 560px;
      background-position: 65% center;

      &__inner {
        min-height: 560px;
      }

      &__title {
        font-size: 34px;
      }

      &__lead {
        font-size: 15px;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
